Very very good and incredibly easy. (took about 10 minutes from start to finish) As suggested, I increased the sauce a little bit and it turned out great. Great for weekday dinner but also good enough for guests.

Rating: 3
Incredibly easy. I substituted scallions and half-and-half for the shallots and cream since I didn't want to run back to the store. I served it with Jasmine rice and a dry white wine. If it was this good with scallions and half-and-half, I will HAVE to try it with the shallots and the cream! One suggestion: Make extra sauce. The sauce seems to disappear quickly once the eating begins.

